name: MultiKeyTest
description: Unit tests for the MultiKey class, focusing on constructors, equality, serialization, and hash code.

nested_classes.name: DerivedMultiKey
nested_classes.description: A derived class extending MultiKey with additional methods to get the first and second keys.

nested_classes.name: SystemHashCodeSimulatingKey
nested_classes.description: A class simulating a system hash code change after deserialization.

test_cases.description: Tests the constructors of MultiKey with different numbers of arguments and an array constructor.

test_cases.name: testHashCode
